node.text:
Trip To Namibia Competition! 🐘 
.
We are giving you a chance to win a 2-week desert elephant adventure to Namibia, Africa and learn first hand about the critically endangered desert elephant population. Expect to get your hands dirty, learn about conservation, make new friends, sleep under the stars and enjoy the natural, beautiful surroundings.
To Enter:
1. Follow @nuii_icecream_global
2. Upload an image to Instagram, tagging @nuii_icecream_global and #MyNuiiAdventure
Winners selection to be judged on originality, quality, unexpected locations and creativity We can’t wait to see what you guys share.
Competiton ends on 6th September 2021
Good luck!
#MyNuiiAdventure #IceCreamAdventure #AD T&C’s apply
(This giveaway is not sponsored by Instagram)
